<h2 class="bold font-l">Black Bowser's Castle</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The clouds part revealing the castle floating in the air. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Ominous Floating Building</span> </h3>
</div>
